itedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T05:08:59.000Z","msg":"依家告暴動告到好似公眾地方行為不檢咁<br />\n一條咁重嘅罪公廁過公廁<br />\n酷刑罪好似恐龍淨係知有條咁嘅罪但永遠唔會見撚到咁<br />\n重話法治未死條over my dead body 死撚咗去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a48b467f3d92cc9d010012a84aeb8a1adc5b4a7","tid":1781292,"uid":228995,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"4ab221c7c39163b86462f3dcfa50fa7b53444cf0","tid":1781292,"uid":31022,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"quote":{"pid":"14419dac6a0207299c75fceff6bc8da573c51a5c","tid":1781292,"uid":228995,"like":9,"dislike":39,"score":-30,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T05:03:40.000Z","msg":"唔好執著字眼<br />\n<br />\n重要係刑期"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T05:07:12.000Z","msg":"《侵害人身罪條例》 第17條（意圖造成身體嚴重傷害而傷人，俗稱「傷人17」）作起訴，最高可判處終身監禁。"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T05:09:36.000Z","msg":"因為單嘢事後先告<br />\n<br />\n傷者應該無得驗傷<br />\n<br />\n告傷人17應該判唔到終身<br />\n<br />\n但宜家條控罪證據更易入<br />\n<br />\n睇你點睇"},{"pid":"45ed5924a22ff82aada8f1a6220bc843dae2b7ae","tid":1781292,"uid":195995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T05:10:26.000Z","msg":"點解會拒絕拎創傷報告？"},{"pid":"30947d881ea92a6e53c44f51e0d344d4838b37ca","tid":1781292,"uid":121985,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T05:10:36.000Z","msg":"係酷刑呀屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb99750cc33cd50d0b849e77c9869f949001aae0","tid":1781292,"uid":155682,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T05:12:31.000Z","msg":"其實控罪刑責越高係越要求高, 比較難鋤得死, 兼夾可能多咗抗辯理據, 最緊要入到佢罪, 坐返三五年, 上訴又唔成功果隻, 想一二十年甚至終身真係太大想頭."},{"pid":"c2560b8b917aafe1d78307d6ddc852b7ee5e68f7","tid":1781292,"uid":169665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T05:15:00.000Z","msg":"咁樣檢控難度高咗，定罪又難左呢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e864a529d3877df1f39